Package se.miun.itm.input.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DimensionHelper
    A wrapper for dimensional information for a parameter; each parameter has a dimensional default setup, defined by an instance of this type.
    Document
    A wrapper class that wraps third party library classes, in order to not make users directly depend on them, and due to the restrictions of third party class exposure to service consumers.
    Ranges
    Each numeric parameter (implicitly) defines a range of valid values.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Numeric
    Numeric is the service enum that supplies lower and upper extrema for all numeric values, and supports the random creation of numeric values of all supported kinds, given range restrictions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InPUTException
    The generic exception, that handles all kind of exceptions.
